---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import { SITE_TITLE } from '../consts';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<BaseHead title={`About - ${SITE_TITLE}`} description="About Kristian Bjornebraten - Infrastructure Engineer, Cloud Architect, and DevOps enthusiast" />
		<style>
			main {
				width: 720px;
				max-width: calc(100% - 2em);
				margin: auto;
				padding: 3em 1em;
			}
			.about-header {
				text-align: center;
				margin-bottom: 3rem;
			}
			.about-avatar {
				width: 180px;
				height: 180px;
				border-radius: 50%;
				border: 3px solid var(--color-accent);
				margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
			}
			.about-content {
				line-height: 1.8;
				font-size: 1.1rem;
				color: var(--color-text-main);
			}
			h1 {
				font-size: 2.5rem;
				margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
				color: var(--color-text-main);
			}
			.tagline {
				color: var(--color-text-muted);
				font-size: 1.1rem;
				margin-bottom: 2rem;
			}
			h2 {
				margin-top: 2.5rem;
				margin-bottom: 1rem;
				font-size: 1.4rem;
				color: var(--color-accent);
				border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);
				padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
			}
			p {
				margin-bottom: 1.25em;
			}
			a {
				color: var(--color-accent);
				text-decoration: none;
			}
			a:hover {
				text-decoration: underline;
			}
			ul {
				margin-bottom: 1.5em;
				padding-left: 1.5em;
			}
			li {
				margin-bottom: 0.5em;
			}
			strong {
				color: var(--color-text-main);
				font-weight: 600;
			}
			.highlight {
				background: var(--color-bg-alt);
				padding: 1.5rem;
				border-radius: 8px;
				border-left: 3px solid var(--color-accent);
				margin: 2rem 0;
			}
			.tech-tags {
				display: flex;
				flex-wrap: wrap;
				gap: 0.5rem;
				margin-top: 1rem;
			}
			.tech-tag {
				background: var(--color-bg-alt);
				color: var(--color-text-muted);
				padding: 0.25rem 0.75rem;
				border-radius: 20px;
				font-size: 0.85rem;
				border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
			}
		</style>
	</head>
	<body>
		<Header />
		<main>
			<div class="about-header">
				<img src="/avatar.png" alt="Kristian Bjornebraten" class="about-avatar" />
				<h1>Kristian Bjornebraten</h1>
				<p class="tagline">Infrastructure Engineer · Cloud Architect · DevOps Enthusiast</p>
			</div>

			<section class="about-content">
				<p>
					With <strong>13 years of experience in IT</strong>, I've built extensive knowledge across complex IT infrastructure. 
					In recent years, I've specialized in <strong>cloud technology, DevOps, Infrastructure as Code (IaC), operations, 
					application management, client management, and technical leadership</strong>.
				</p>

				<div class="highlight">
					When I'm not architecting cloud solutions, you'll find me <strong>vibe coding</strong> late into the night—headphones on, 
					coffee in hand, building side projects like <a href="https://tidwerk.com">TidWerk</a>. I'm deep into the 
					<strong>MCP (Model Context Protocol) server</strong> ecosystem, exploring how AI agents can supercharge developer workflows. 
					Yes, I'm that kind of nerd.
				</div>

				<h2>What I Do</h2>
				<p>
					Most recently, I worked as an <strong>Infrastructure Engineer and Delivery Manager</strong>, 
					helping strengthen enterprise Azure cloud platforms. As an architect, I focus on designing, 
					developing, and troubleshooting solutions that ensure secure and efficient communication—both within Azure 
					and between cloud and on-premises systems. I implement solutions meeting strict security and scalability 
					requirements while ensuring compliance with zone models and policies.
				</p>
				<p>
					As Delivery Manager, I take responsibility for delivering cloud-based solutions with emphasis on time management, 
					cost efficiency, and alignment with business objectives. Through agile methodologies and DevOps best practices, 
					I optimize processes and strengthen teams' capacity to deliver reliable solutions.
				</p>

				<h2>Experience Highlights</h2>
				<ul>
					<li><strong>Platform Engineer</strong> — Designed, developed, and tested Terraform code, contributing to architecture and technical assessments</li>
					<li><strong>Tech Lead</strong> — Led infrastructure teams and managed hybrid platforms</li>
					<li><strong>IaC Developer</strong> — Terraform development for critical infrastructure in regulated industries</li>
					<li><strong>Cloud Operator</strong> — Azure operations and continuous process improvement</li>
				</ul>

				<h2>Tech Stack</h2>
				<p>I'm most at home with:</p>
				<div class="tech-tags">
					<span class="tech-tag">Azure</span>
					<span class="tech-tag">Terraform</span>
					<span class="tech-tag">Kubernetes</span>
					<span class="tech-tag">DevOps</span>
					<span class="tech-tag">TypeScript</span>
					<span class="tech-tag">Svelte</span>
					<span class="tech-tag">Python</span>
					<span class="tech-tag">Go</span>
					<span class="tech-tag">CI/CD</span>
					<span class="tech-tag">MCP Servers</span>
				</div>

				<h2>How I Work</h2>
				<p>
					I'm <strong>productive, service-minded, analytical, and detail-oriented</strong>. I work in a structured and 
					goal-oriented manner to ensure tasks are completed in line with both technical and business expectations. 
					Whether it's designing enterprise infrastructure or hacking on personal projects at 2 AM, I bring the same 
					level of dedication and curiosity.
				</p>

				<h2>Let's Connect</h2>
				<p>
					I'm always open to discussing cloud architecture, DevOps practices, or nerding out about the latest in 
					AI-assisted development. Check out my <a href="/blog">blog</a> for thoughts on tech, or reach out if 
					you want to collaborate.
				</p>
			</section>
		</main>
		<Footer />
	</body>
</html>
